{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315400/extras/banner-ezgif.com-resize.gif?t=1732283751\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The forest was once peaceful, but now plants and animals are at war!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Become a forest guardian fairy and set off on a one-day journey to save the forest tainted by a dark curse. Intense battles await from bright morning to sunset and into the dark night.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this prologue, you can enjoy 3 morning battles that awaken the forest and 1 battle at twilight as the sun sets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315400/extras/battle.gif?t=1732283751\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Defend Your Base and Defeat the Enemy Boss</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To cleanse the cursed forest and call for allies, you\u2019ll need a base called the \u201cMushtower.\u201d Protect it from waves of enemies. Enemies will keep coming until their boss is defeated. Use your limited mana to summon animal allies and push back with skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315400/extras/GIF_Deck_Eng.gif?t=1732283751\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Grow Your Deck</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From morning to night, enemies get stronger. To win, your allies need to grow too. Collect better animal cards and give animals <strong>hats</strong> with power boosts. Skill cards and magical artifacts are also part of your strategy for victory!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315400/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732283751","background_raw":"